Sentencas: Crystal structure, high temperature oxygen nonstoichiometry and transport properties of two members of La1-xSrxCo1-y-zFeyNizO3-delta group of perovskite type oxides are presented.
Titulo: Oxygen Nonstoichiometry and Transport Properties of Selected La1-xSrxCo1-y-zFeyNizO3-δ Perovskites

Sentencas: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.6Ni0.2O3-delta and La0.9Sr0.1Co1/3Fe1/3Ni1/3O3-delta compositions possess high electrical conductivity at high temperatures in air.
Titulo: Oxygen Nonstoichiometry and Transport Properties of Selected La1-xSrxCo1-y-zFeyNizO3-δ Perovskites

Sentencas: However, the observed characteristics of the electrical conductivity as a function of the oxygen partial pressure for these materials are significantly different.
Titulo: Oxygen Nonstoichiometry and Transport Properties of Selected La1-xSrxCo1-y-zFeyNizO3-δ Perovskites

Sentencas: A discussion of the observed effects is provided, which shows strong correlation between chemical composition, crystal structure, oxygen nonstoichiometry and the observed transport properties.
Titulo: Oxygen Nonstoichiometry and Transport Properties of Selected La1-xSrxCo1-y-zFeyNizO3-δ Perovskites

Sentencas: An interesting phenomenon related to an irreversible oxygenation of the quenched La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.6Ni0.2O3-delta samples was observed.
Titulo: Oxygen Nonstoichiometry and Transport Properties of Selected La1-xSrxCo1-y-zFeyNizO3-δ Perovskites

Sentencas: This reaction takes place at 200-300 degrees C range which is well below a typical nonstoichiometry related reactions.
Titulo: Oxygen Nonstoichiometry and Transport Properties of Selected La1-xSrxCo1-y-zFeyNizO3-δ Perovskites

Sentencas: A possible explanation of this effect is discussed.
Titulo: Oxygen Nonstoichiometry and Transport Properties of Selected La1-xSrxCo1-y-zFeyNizO3-δ Perovskites
